What is this:

   This is linux hack port of ML_SONY.
   ML_SONY is winamp plugin that support sony network players.
   see also http://sourceforge.net/projects/mlsony

   'sonydb' is a maintenance application for sony network players.

License:
	BSD license


Build instruction for old_sonydb
```
sudo apt install make autotools-dev libid3-dev automake gcc g++ gawk
$ ./autogen.sh
$ ./configure
$ make
$ sudo make install
```
